Exercise 1:

Step 1: Take the chicken to the other side of the river and come back alone.
Step 2: Take the fox to the other side and come back with the chicken.
Step 3: Leave the chicken on the first side and bring the seeds to the fox side.
Step 4: Take the chicken to the other side.


Exercise 2:

Take 'fruit' from O+A {
  If (fruit == apple){
    O+A = A;
    O = O+A;
    A = 0;
    }
    
  Else {
    O+A = O;
    A = O+A;
    O = A;
  }
 }
